#

Fluffy Pancakes with Maple Syrup and Fresh Berries

25 min
$5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

GlutenDairyEggs

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

BreakfastEasyQuickSweet

Description

Light and fluffy pancakes drizzled with sweet maple syrup and topped with fresh, juicy berries for a delightful breakfast treat.

Ingredients

  • all-purpose flour: 1 cup
  • milk: 1 cup
  • egg: 1
  • baking powder: 2 tsp
  • sugar: 2 tbsp
  • salt: 1/2 tsp
  • butter (melted): 2 tbsp
  • maple syrup: to taste
  • fresh berries (strawberries, blueberries, etc.): 1 cup
